      "retweeted_tweet_id": null,
      "text": "Online exploitation or abuse of a kid or teen is NEVER the victim’s fault. If you suspect an online crime: \n\n1️⃣ Don’t pay or send more images if threatened. \n2️⃣ Save everything — don’t delete messages. \n3️⃣ Report the crime ASAP. \n4️⃣ Support is always available for victims. \n\nGet help at: https://t.co/CBnlY004QT #Know2Protect",
