      "reply_to_account": null,
      "reply_to_account_id": null,
      "quoted_tweet_id": null,
      "retweeted_tweet_id": null,
      "text": "When in doubt, reach out and report. If you suspect a kid or teen is being exploited or abused online, contact law enforcement ASAP — whether the suspected person is an adult, teen or another child. \n\nFile a report for any of the following:  \n 🚩 Online harassment that feels unsafe \n 🚩 Pressure for nude images, videos or livestreams \n 🚩 Threats of sextortion for more pics and/or money \n 🚩 Creation or sharing of child sexual abuse material \n\nLearn more at: https://t.co/CBnlY004QT #DigitalSafety #OnlineSafety #Know2Protect",
      "text_resolved": "When in doubt, reach out and report. If you suspect a kid or teen is being exploited or abused online, contact law enforcement ASAP — whether the suspected person is an adult, teen or another child. \n\nFile a report for any of the following:  \n 🚩 Online harassment that feels unsafe \n 🚩 Pressure for nude images, videos or livestreams \n 🚩 Threats of sextortion for more pics and/or money \n 🚩 Creation or sharing of child sexual abuse material \n\nLearn more at: http://dhs.gov/know2protect/how-to-report #DigitalSafety #OnlineSafety #Know2Protect",
      "lang": "en",
